			<div class="content" id="post-content-4707544">
									

<p>Happy pride month, motherfuckers, from ARD and ch00bakka.</p>
<p>This tale officially introduces Rukmini Mahakali into the Cool War universe &#8212; a freelance assassin with a Master's of Assassination degree from the Rhode Island School of Demolition and a screwed up ethical code to boot. Lives a morally unsatisfying but hedonistically unrivaled life in backdoor soho. Wears platform crocs, bell bottoms ironically, and an army surplus jacket. Think Travis 'Catra' Touchdown. Go nuts.</p>
<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599153641" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;">Randomini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599153641" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rumetzen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(209204); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=209204&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599153641" alt="rumetzen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=209204)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rumetzen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(209204); return false;">rumetzen</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599153641" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span> for their critique.</p>
<p>The appropriate theme, of course, is one <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zuHcuEenwp8">Ideal for Violence</a>.</p>

